FuncDef: The reset aaa online-fail-record command clears the statistics about all user online failure records.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
To facilitate the recording of user online failure records during a certain period, run the reset aaa online-fail-record command to clear statistics about all user online failure records.
The records cannot be restored after being cleared. Exercise caution when running the
reset aaa online-fail-record command.
